9 October 2019 Government held a successful launch of the new District Development Model in Lusikisiki, Eastern Cape on September 17, 2019, and it will roll out the second pilot of the model on October 18, 2019 in eThekwini Metro, Kwa Zulu-Natal. Members of the media who wish to cover the roll out of the model are requested to apply for accreditation by filing in the attached registration form and send their details to Takalani Mukwevho on takalanim@gcis.gov.za or Nomzamo Zondi on nomzamo@gcis.gov.za , all fields must be completed. The deadline for the submission of the details is Tuesday, 15 October 2019 at 12h00. The details for the collection of accreditation will be communicated at a later stage. Enquiries:Phumla WilliamsCell: 083 501 0139